*************************************************
*                                               *
*                RSA ALGORTIHM                  *
*                                               *
*                                               *
*************************************************
(1)	Generate keys
(2)	Encrypt message
(3)	Decrypt message
(4)	Exit

This program is the implementation of the RSA algorithm in the C programing lenguage using the gmp (gnu multiprecicion library) for arbitrary length numbers. The program receive as input a file with the number in base 10 to be encrypted or decrypted.

WARNING: The <time.h> library sometimes gives inconsistent time measurements in windows OS.
